{"tid":1171784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那唐山一化工廠突發火災 濃煙滾滾疑似爆炸","createTime":"2019-05-26T03:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T04:03:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17ad88970faa18a18e170e160820b2f30a3ade06","tid":1171784,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"5月24日（週五）上午，位於唐山曹妃甸的河北龍成煤綜合利用有限公司發生火災，該事故造成2死6傷。<br />\n <br />\n據大陸網民24日爆料稱，河北唐山曹妃甸一家化工廠發生火災，現場疑似爆炸。<br />\n <br />\n當天下午，當地官方發布消息，稱是河北龍成煤綜合利用有限公司發生火災，目前事故原因正在調查中。<br />\n <br />\n據官方通報，此次火災，共有8名企業職工不同程度受傷，其中2人因傷勢過重，經搶救無效死亡。"},{"pid":"573af91de6158321c50bba10c05e86e7a0562b4a","tid":1171784,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"到共匪亡國前都唔會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b1f1f887df3b5f3bdb0266a0d86a833945a69c","tid":1171784,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"共有8名企業職工不同程度受傷，其中2人因傷勢過重，經搶救無效死亡<br />\n<br />\n交足戲，respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就算懷疑係人為自爆都奈你唔何<br />\n<br />\n之前啲自爆0傷亡好冇誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856807abdb51e3d7b6ca6208d7415d0669f3858d","tid":1171784,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:03:04.000Z","msg":"中國爆炸終於有人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}